title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Sugars & Sugar Confectionery
description: Imports of Intra EU - Sugars & Sugar Confectionery in the United Kingdom increased to 75.51 GBP Million in September from 71.99 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Sugars & Sugar Confectionery in the United Kingdom averaged 43.75 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 86.25 GBP Million in January of 2019 and a record low of 13.49 GBP Million in January of 1999. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Sugars & Sugar Confectionery.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
